org.gbif.api.model.registry.eml.curatorial

Class CuratorialUnitComposite

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.api.model.registry.eml.curatorial.CuratorialUnit
      • org.gbif.api.model.registry.eml.curatorial.CuratorialUnitComposite
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class CuratorialUnitComposite
extends CuratorialUnit
    Composite class, combining fields from CuratorialUnitCount and CuratorialUnitRange for simpler parsing of curatorial units, since both count and range types share the same root element.
